n all Federal Government Securities. Commenting on the appointment, the Chief Executive Officer of CSL Stockbrokers, Mr. Abiodun Fagbulu, described the development as another milestone in the commitment of the firm to be the investment management services provider of choice in sub-Saharan Africa, driven by deep market knowledge and global standard investment management expertise. CSL Stockbrokers Limited (an associate company of FCMB Plc), one of Nigeriaâ€™s largest stockbroking firms is organizing its first international investorsâ€™ conference aimed at bridging information gap between quoted companies on the Nigerian Stock Exchange (NSE) and local and international investors. September 21, 2009 In "Business" Stanbic IBTC Stockbrokers has described as unfounded the claims that its appointment as government stockbroker for FGN bonds will make it possible for it to poach the customers of other stockbroking firms. February 4, 2013 In "Finance" The appointment of Stanbic IBTC Stockbrokers, a subsidiary of Stanbic IBTC Holdings Plc as stockbroker to the Federal Government of Nigeria will translate into increased retail investors’ participation in primary and secondary markets of Federal Government bonds and ultimately help to deepen Nigeria’s bond market. November 22, 2012 In "Business"